Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了 我以为吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在棺材里面睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你却是哪里都能睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还能做人类的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也帮你睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你睡个永远都不能够醒的觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手吧 如果你还有那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快要天光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这井里面的第三个早晨就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500, 0)}第六夜 井底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果敢过来我就杀掉这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我好不容易得到的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会这么被你抓住而放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生已经失踪三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却一个人在这里吃饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的晚出早归 并不是很奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是连今天已经是第三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的 我已经派人在找了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个被紫藤追的男人也有在调查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要休息一下 理保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全都没睡过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我可以更像紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以控制力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟过去也只有碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最担心的是那个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是第三天了 非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这工地里是不可能听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让这个人的伤口裂开的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔走 拔掉这讨厌的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我也许会出去叫人过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很痛所以我是讲真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想和我在这冰冷黑暗的井底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起死掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 吸血鬼是不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该快要饿得支持不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要这样眼睁睁看着她死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这冷血的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吧 反正她都快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我将她吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连一根头发都不剩的吃掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱的恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸人血的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要得到人类身体的夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和想吸人血的吸血鬼的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么差别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再去攻击人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经偷偷的活了那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼的本性多少还是知道一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在夜间活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你袒护人类有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我原本是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我应该还拥有人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为自己还是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这样想的大概只有你一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走别人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸走人类的血的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁会承认你是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不能存在于光的下面的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾崎浩二 34岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天前就失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他 不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有什么原因被夜灵给附身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子那方面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那方面一点消息都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不是这里的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在应该会有人出现请求搜查的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一点都不可以放松
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我并不想把你牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我好不容易才得到的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想失去他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很棒 活着这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样可以和你谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真的很痛快受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想继续活下去而已 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以帮我把它拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔感觉很痛痛的受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要帮我把它拿出来你就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:11:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就可以脱离这黑暗井底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这剑拉出来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会被一个小孩那么容易就拔出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…我要吃掉你 吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼是不死身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来证明这是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我所受到的痛苦才不是这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我把你的脖子给折断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在发高烧 也许是肺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讲得对吧 是你阻止她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子来向我求救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子会死 是你害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你做一点补偿 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吸她的血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是件很简单的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被吸血她就能变成吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是得到肺炎也不会死亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你也可以得到解放 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做就可以救回那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用再考虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不再对人类下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所看见的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是个小学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经找过十年份的资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再往上找也没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是不死心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也许我会看漏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帮她吸血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在还没错过时机之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为了要救那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也饿得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不可能违背本能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快吸血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！闭嘴！闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 因为今后需要用到那种技术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有了技术就可以治愈流行病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然大家一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将会赐给你永远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起守护爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人在永远的时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要照你的本能意识去做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被选中的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用去在意死和时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我到底是做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不用对人类讲抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要让他们重生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那些被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 一个新生命的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和妈妈一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把我给唤回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路只剩下二条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条就是自灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一条就是吸那孩子的血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果最后你能承认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我同样是夜族我就很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 吸血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么 别打歪主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再犯同样的错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饿疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘记还有另一个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是可能让这孩子活下去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将那个孩子送到医院去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子的搜索令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三十年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子和那时搜索的照片一点都没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近这些奇怪的地方动作真快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这个地方已经活了五百年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些申请搜索的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是那时和我一起生活的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先谢谢你让我看场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻的吸血鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡到了一只全身湿透的小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它躺下吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给它温暖的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当作一生的宠物守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮流的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在危险的时候把小猫踢飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲…就是那么回事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Night Walker 第七夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲与儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想要…什么永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波に漂う　月の光　昏睡の中　月の光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走る　独り　暗い　空を　あなたに逢えるなら
